      <description>檢查憑證的指令如下 檢查憑證的指令可以用-text與-noout來查看憑證細節: openssl x509 -in my.crt -text -noout 輸出類似: Certificate: Data: Version: 3 (0x2) Serial Number: 3147495682089747350 (0x2bae26a58f090396) Signature Algorithm: sha256WithRSAEncryption Issuer: CN=kubernetes Validity Not Before: Feb 11 05:39:19</description>
    </item>
